Sandberg


                    The swedish jewelery brand Sandberg Sweden was founded in 2000 by Staffan Sandberg. Sandberg's creates innovative and exclusive pieces of jewellery. The hand drawn turtle is their trademark and symbolizes a long and happy life. All jewelries are made in Sweden.

                    Read more �




